Key Takeaways from Journey Mapping  Core Product Needs Candidate Dashboard Is Critical Needs to clearly communicate next steps, job match progress, interview outcomes, and hiring manager connections. Demo Video Add a short demo video explaining Sally’s role, domain focus, and how it benefits users. Build Trust Through Proof Showcase testimonials and success stories from users with similar backgrounds to increase credibility.  Post-Interview Engagement Add a Progress Tracker A visual indicator that shows completed steps and upcoming stages. Improve Candidate Retention Use email, WhatsApp nudges, and small interactive updates to maintain engagement after the interview. Feedback Loop Enhancements Provide interview feedback that includes performance summaries and human-reviewed insights on soft skills.   Tools for Growth and Personalization Portfolio Linkage Support Allow candidates to connect GitHub, Notion, Behance, and other platforms to highlight real work. Skill-Based Assessment Ideas Explore domain-relevant assessments that evaluate ability beyond past job titles or education. Content-Led Empowerment Offer educational content like salary benchmarks, negotiation tips, and interview preparation resources. Introduce Sally Co-Pilot (Future Concept) A guidance layer that helps candidates understand the system, prepare better, and feel supported at every step.   Recruiter-Side Insights Highlight Why a Candidate Matches Show how candidates align with job descriptions (e.g., matched skills, soft skills, experience fit). Recruiter Testimonials Build Confidence Use hiring manager quotes and case studies to demonstrate success and attract more recruiter trust.

Key Takeaways Own the Interview Prep and Mock Interview Journeys (more interactive experience) Introduce a Smart Dashboard to organize and guide the job search where candidates can save jobs from all over the internet in our platform Work on a Candidate’s Dashboard with all the information about Applications, Interviews and Shortlisting (plus nudges to keep them engaged e.g. “You’ve completed 3/5 Application goals for the day,” Offer Real-Time Resume Optimization with JD match scores Launch a Personalized AI Assistant/Co-pilot to guide users continuously Enhance Onboarding for instant value and engagement
